# Strongswan build RPM

This is a mashup of Strongswan 5.7.x for CentOS6.

The SPEC file is taken from the EPEL distribution SRC RPM

https://rpmfind.net/linux/RPM/epel/6/x86_64/Packages/s/strongswan-5.4.0-2.el6.x86_64.html

https://rpmfind.net/linux/RPM/epel/7/x86_64/Packages/s/strongswan-5.7.2-1.el7.x86_64.html

## Untested

You have been warned.

## Build

```
docker-rpm-builder dir --download-sources alanfranz/drb-epel-6-x86-64:latest . /tmp/rpms
```

## See also

https://github.com/docker-rpm-builder/docker-rpm-builder#installation


